{"tid":1760103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[大家期待的結果終會出現] 制裁名單料短期難出現 在美港人籲港美續分工合作","createTime":"2019-11-28T03:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T04:11:45.000Z","uid":44562,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e93fc032031f1c2bdb3cb730820830fb18225e43","tid":1760103,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:57:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191128/60318782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191128%2F60318782&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=eb52c692\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191128%2F60318782&h=e4631ad6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191128/60318782</a><br />\n<br />\n對於港人期待看到某些<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">官員或警察受到制裁</span></span></strong>，楊錦霞直言，這畫面不會短期內出現。因為國會距離年底休會只剩十個工作天。即使曾有人舉報，列出應制裁名單，當中每個人做過甚麼，是否足以加以制裁，尚需當局查證，而司法程序需時。<br />\n<br />\n不過，她補充表示，國會尚有另外一條由共和黨參議員霍利（Josh Hawley）提出的制裁法案《Hong Kong Be Water Act》，所以港人只需保持耐性，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家期待的結果終會出現</span></span></strong>。而香港逆權運動一日未完，HKDC亦會繼續向美國政界施壓。<br />\n<br />\nCharles認為港人的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter國際戰線非常有用</span></span></strong>，因為reweet和like的數目越高，越能保持香港成為話題。他期望美港兩邊可以繼續分工合作，香港團隊負責帶起輿論，而美國團隊就負責和當地政界接觸，起事半功倍之效。<br />\nCharles亦希望港人可以更多支持HKDC，因為在美國進行游說工程繁複又花錢，而HKDC的眾籌至今尚未達標。"},{"pid":"1296c5272f00dd1e33ecffc1e7f2ca3fd332b487","tid":1760103,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"【推到全球制裁】香港人權及民主法案 制裁Wishlist<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1759895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1759895</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9c9dca738794896042d44963355d8c8089c0c5f7","tid":1760103,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"1. regina ip"},{"pid":"1cbd557717766e627f6ce5341e00ff353699fd6c","tid":1760103,"uid":246023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:06:56.000Z","msg":"推堅持"},{"pid":"0e705907667b2698d42ba1731843a6badddd8ce8","tid":1760103,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:07:00.000Z","msg":"而家只係一個foundation<br />\n好似得到一個容器咁，要慢慢裝"},{"pid":"7cdc6db9eb70aa8a7f76cadb9bd9ce0eafa05599","tid":1760103,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c9dca738794896042d44963355d8c8089c0c5f7","tid":1760103,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"1. regina ip"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"2. 林鄭<br />\n3. 李家超<br />\n4. 鄭若驊"},{"pid":"246e2b5114c65844b74f87c6c5c943331e893cdb","tid":1760103,"uid":276821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:11:45.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Be Water Act 唔係人權法案lite版? 定還是有唔同細節在內"}]}